Comment: early Miocene - mix of P. rugosa and H. elegans and A. semicribratus indicate middle slope
early Miocene - most specimens indicate upper to middle slope but frequent B. jarvisi indicates no shallower than lower slope
Benthics given only cursory analysis in this sample
basal Miocene; influx of shallow-water spp. including nodosariids and Anomalinoides; influx of agglutinates; possible displacement of sediment
